{"trip_id":"1997-france-1997-amiens-loire-bourges-conques","epigraph":{"quote":"We have seen a heron, kingfisher, large fish, minnows, lizards, a deer, many coppiced sweet chestnuts (ground for flour)."},"moments":[{"seq":2,"place_id":"folkestone-eurotunnel","lon":1.1156,"lat":51.093,"place":"Folkestone (Eurotunnel)","date":"1997-07-29","role":"crossing_terminal","quote":"We had lunch on the Shuttle. No water can be poured, or washing up or coffee.","images":[]},{"seq":3,"place_id":"amiens-france","lon":2.2956951,"lat":49.8941708,"place":"Amiens, France","date":"1997-07-29","role":"main_stop","quote":"The clear drop of the slender pillars from ceiling to floor along the nave is spectacular.","images":[]},{"seq":4,"place_id":"loeuilly-france","lon":2.2018115,"lat":49.7715245,"place":"Loeuilly, France","date":"1997-07-29","role":"overnight_base","quote":"Between the canal & the lake were rows & rows of poplars. Very pretty restful, glinting sunlight, fish, frogs.","images":[]},{"seq":5,"place_id":"l-isle-adam-france","lon":2.2186324,"lat":49.1125294,"place":"L'Isle-Adam, France","date":"1997-07-29","role":"overnight_base","quote":"Good clean loos, free showers. Cement ping pong tables + nets.","images":[]},{"seq":6,"place_id":"paris-france","lon":2.320041,"lat":48.8588897,"place":"Paris, France","date":"1997-07-29","role":"main_stop","quote":"Simon did an amazing Tour de Force driving across the roundabout at the L'Arc de Triomphe.","images":[{"src":"media/1997-france-1997-amiens-loire-bourges-conques/A_0204_R_2.webp","w":900,"h":708,"caption":"Chateau de la Ferté, St. Aubin","type":"sketch"},{"src":"media/1997-france-1997-amiens-loire-bourges-conques/A_0204_R_1.webp","w":797,"h":451,"caption":"Ascension de la Tour Eiffel","type":"ticket"}]},{"seq":7,"place_id":"la-ferte-saint-aubin-france","lon":1.9442053,"lat":47.7169399,"place":"La Ferté-Saint-Aubin, France","date":"1997-07-29","role":"overnight_base","quote":"A man has made it his life's work to renovate it for th